-- Vale to Pay Up to 4.5 Billion Reais in Royalties, Reuters Says
-- B y   P e t e r   M i l l a r d
-- 2012-07-18T22:19:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-18/vale-to-pay-up-to-4-5-billion-reais-in-royalties-reuters-says.html
Vale SA, the world’s second-biggest
mining company, has completed negotiations with  Brazil ’s
National Mineral Production Department over unpaid royalties and
has agreed to pay up to 4.5 billion reais ($2.2 billion),
 Reuters  reported, citing unnamed people.  To contact the reporter on this story:
